{"tid":581533,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"五個月喇","createTime":"2018-03-05T12:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T14:34:14.000Z","uid":45991,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"62f566f4cb60874bf95b9660ef89cfcf169b91f7","tid":581533,"uid":45991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:05:35.000Z","msg":"有無人會好似我咁<br />\n比人飛左<br />\n自己去旅行都會買禮物比個EX<br />\n重要EX已經有第個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分左手五個月<br />\n我第一次完全無興趣無心機識異性<br />\n話放低話左幾個月<br />\n身邊朋友都唔再理我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點先可以放低到<br />\n男人老狗咁婆媽其實真係好肉酸<br />\n我知真係肉酸 但我就係走唔出<br />\n自己一個無野做就會睇我地以前拍落既片<br />\n我地笑得好開心 好有默契<br />\n您錄比我既歌 又走音又甩KEY 但我都覺得好好聽<br />\n望返轉頭 其實我對您一啲都唔好<br />\n點解您咁錫我<br />\n同您一齊過真係教識我好多野<br />\n我唔會再為左淡氣唔理您喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果日您肯聽我電話係呢五個月黎最開心既一日喇<br />\nily<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5644f2efcc5a56a62b220402a8c6e0025353010a","tid":581533,"uid":161205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"巴打你咁似講緊我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33630913cb459fc341b7c6d5d7f93ca890cfea46","tid":581533,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5644f2efcc5a56a62b220402a8c6e0025353010a","tid":581533,"uid":161205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:08:23.000Z",